# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Files that must NOT be published to GitHub
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Private business context (daily-update skill) ---
**/daily-update/assets/search_context.md

# --- Generated reports (may contain sensitive analysis) ---
daily-update-reports/
*-daily-update.md
*-daily-update.docx

# --- Secrets / credentials ---
.env
.env.*
*.key
*secret*
*credentials*
openrouter*.txt

# --- Word / Office lock & temp files ---
~$*.docx
~$*.doc
*.tmp

# --- Python cache ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Editor / IDE ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
